"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"通常刑事都係咁，比如傷人加個襲擊做交替<br />\n審到最尾如果重啲嗰條唔成立，就要睇埋Present咗嘅evidence夠唔夠入條輕啲嘅"},{"pid":"19d7688e2478195b4391d7aef8149aa6737065d3","tid":2281144,"uid":33373,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"255f8f11ca3ff79fef8ae3fd1f6c218321d22ece","tid":2281144,"uid":25468,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"個交替罪係留黎等個縱火罪入唔到嘅時候再告，根本為左打壓而非為公義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"普通法原則下<br />\n唔可以一罪兩控"},{"pid":"8a85f3367ee04ff3cb93f8406c2b96b1970b77ae","tid":2281144,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"黨官扯貓尾？"},{"pid":"b9423b2ad47d874620ce24b5b504f7e418d99c63","tid":2281144,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"xx-large\">傀儡</span>"},{"pid":"8ff911b58dad4c2a87fb911cbc93887fc64ea5ee","tid":2281144,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862e0331f1cec644706ca61c60d8bb953e8a523c","tid":2281144,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8f2369555dc92198e14186b534e605d4b33fd2","tid":2281144,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:32:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11215&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=8109f2e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11215</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿三庭<br />\n#葉佐文法官 #0815元朗 #審訊<br />\n<br />\n劉（56）<br />\n🛑曾經還押逾一星期<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n企圖縱火<br />\n(交替控罪：刑事恐嚇)<br />\n<br />\n審訊：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11212&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=9b633313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11212</a><br />\n<br />\n根據新聞報導，被告已認刑事恐嚇‼️‼️<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201111/A3WPWJTPQRAIBEN3CEB5WIFVRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201111%2FA3WPWJTPQRAIBEN3CEB5WIFVRI%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=4d29e59d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201111%2FA3WPWJTPQRAIBEN3CEB5WIFVRI%2F&h=aed89268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201111/A3WPWJTPQRAIBEN3CEB5WIFVRI/</a><br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告一早已考慮認罪，只是控方反對所以才弄到今天，辯方希望可以減足1／3刑期。法庭要求控方好好考慮，及要求律政司書面報告。<br />\n<br />\n法庭指責辯方沒在以往幾次上庭時，跟法庭交代，只是控辯雙方底下商討，因此沒有存檔，亦指責辯方在文件處理上字眼用得不好。<br />\n<br />\n證物留後處理<br />\n<br />\n辯方有保釋申請，希望待星期五再續，保釋申請被拒<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️即時還押‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2020年11月13日星期五區域法院11：00判刑‼️<br />\n<br />\n😞法庭明言大機會即時監禁😞<br />\n（按：劉手足精神徬徨，有點空洞）"},{"pid":"47302f77e6795447a9be7be0c215bd3866901f38","tid":2281144,"uid":69787,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:37:23.000Z","msg":"咁大年紀仲要係會計師都肯企到咁前"},{"pid":"8859135dc52c5d27203b64698853820584acc36b","tid":2281144,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19d7688e2478195b4391d7aef8149aa6737065d3","tid":2281144,"uid":33373,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"255f8f11ca3ff79fef8ae3fd1f6c218321d22ece","tid":2281144,"uid":25468,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"個交替罪係留黎等個縱火罪入唔到嘅時候再告，根本為左打壓而非為公義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"普通法原則下<br />\n唔可以一罪兩控"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim